    <h1>Deinfluencing</h1>
    <p class="description">A social-media movement where creators tell followers <strong>not</strong> to buy overhyped products. It emerged on TikTok in 2023, hit <strong>1 billion+ hashtag views</strong> in months, and permanently changed how consumers evaluate creator recommendations.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
